 Rancho Deluxe (TNT Tuesday at 1 p.m.) is a droll 1975 Frank Perry-Thomas 
McGuane contemporary Western with Jeff Bridges and Sam Waterston as a couple of 
cattle rustlers; co-starring Elizabeth Ashley. 
