FOUR-STAR FILMS; 'THE LONG VOYAGE HOME' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Kevin Thomas 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 This 1940 classic reunited "Stagecoach's" John Ford, John Wayne (pictured, 
with Carmen Morales), Thomas Mitchell and writer Dudley Nichols in a robust yet 
poetic adaptation of four short plays by Eugene O'Neill about men caught up in 
the siren call of the sea. The elegiac sensibilities of Ford and O'Neill mesh 
beautifully.(Bravo Friday at 9:30 a.m. and 11:10 p.m.). 
</P>
