Very Ted," featuring four Ted Baxter episodes of "The Mary Tyler Moore Show." 
</P>
<P>
 Gabe Kaplan plays a cop with a humorous approach to crime fighting on Police 
Story (Monday at 9 a.m. on A&E) 
</P>
<P>
 Ed Asner guests as an aging cop who is ordered to train an ambitious rookie on 
Police Story (Monday at 3 p.m. and Tuesday at 9 a.m. on A&E). 
</P>
