<P>
NAACP EXTENDS EMPLOYEE FURLOUGHS IN BUDGET CRISIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 NAACP officials have extended furloughs for 88 employees for two more weeks as 
it continues to battle financial problems. 
