<P>
JUST THE FACTS: CRUISE SHIP SCORES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cruise ship sanitation scores for some of the ships inspected in August and 
September. A score of 86 or higher indicates acceptable sanitation. 
</P>
<P>
 * Acceptable Arkona: 90 Crystal Harmony: 95 Dolphin IV: 91 Ecstasy: 94 
Fantasy: 94 Fascination: 90 Fiesta Marina: 87 Horizon: 94 Meridian: 95 Nordic 
Prince: 87 Queen Elizabeth 2: 90 Regent Sun: 87 Royal Majesty: 95 Sagafjord: 88 
Seabreeze I: 92 Sea Lion: 94 Silver Cloud: 98 Song of America: 90 Sovereign of 
the Seas: 90 Yorktown Clipper: 93 Zenith: 96 
</P>
<P>
 * UNACCEPTABLE Cunard Countess: 84 Westerdam: 85 
</P>
<P>
 Source: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention 
</P>
