<DOCID> 098324 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 13, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4 
</P>
