<P>
 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Kevin Stipp: 0-0 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. 
HGT. P Velina Gibson Sr. 5-8 G Allison Napier So. 6-3 C Tanya Whitlock Jr. 5-7 
F 04,15,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. P Maria Avila Jr. 5-9 F Liz Lara Sr. 
5-4 G 04,18,05,06,04 TOP NEWCOMERS YR. HGT. P Debbie Arostigue So. 5-6 G Rhonda 
Bell Jr. 5-10 F Maria Fariaz So. 5-6 G Vicky Tapia So. 5-2 G Kathie Vang So. 
