<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL 1994-1995 / CENTURY LEAGUE; ORANGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL: 4-17 LEAGUE: 1-9 
</P>
<P>
 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Chuck Newman: 0-0 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS 
