<TEXT>
<P>
 Kids will busy themselves for more than an hour with an array of activities at 
their very own child-size table with chairs.Coloring with friends or having tea 
parties with their dolls and stuffed animals will be less bothersome for you as 
you'll no longer have to gather a pile of phone books for the kids to sit on.  
</P>
<P>
 In fact, reluctant eaters may even clean their plates when they can dine at 
their own table. 
</P>
<P>
 All three pieces are made from just one sheet of 3/4-inch plywood or pine. 
Step-by-step instructions and full-size traceable patterns make it easy to do. 
Just transfer the pattern onto wood, cut out and assemble. 
