<HEADLINE>
<P>
ANT REPELLENT CLEANS UP THE AREA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 There is a person who often dumps the contents of his car ashtray on the grass 
near (my) curb. 
</P>
<P>
 I used to put them into the gutter, but now I separate the tobacco from the 
filter and put the tobacco into a jar with an equal amount of water. Then I let 
it set in the sun for a few days. It's the best ant repellent I've ever used. I 
circled the stuff around my lemon tree and kept it free of ants. 
</P>
<P>
 LOUIS NEWMAN 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
