other breads, pastries, deli case with sandwiches and picnic items; espresso 
drinks; (707) 433-1913. 
</P>
<P>
 Downtown Bakery, 308A Center St., Healdsburg 95448; crusty bread, croissants, 
focaccia, sticky buns, tarts, cakes, ice cream; (707) 431-2719. 
</P>
